<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/p/books/the-flightless-birds-of-new-hope-farah-naz-rishi/893c09dd4b0dc1af?ean=9781662532290&amp;next=t&amp;next=t" class="external" target="_blank">The Flightless Birds of New Hope</a> <em>by Farah Naz Rishi is available via Lake Union Publishing.</em></span></p><div class="insert-post-ads" style="clear:both;width:100%;margin:0 0 20px 0;"><span>Article continues after advertisement</span><!-- GAM 22020028882/LTHB_lithubcom/Article_Incontent_4 -->
<div data-fuse="Article_Incontent_4"></div></div>
</p>							</div>
