						<h2><a href="https://lithub.com/notable-literary-deaths-in-2025/" title="Notable Literary Deaths in 2025">Notable Literary Deaths in 2025</a></h2>
					</div>
				</div>
											<div class="cell auto tertiary-story">
					<div class="story-img-container">
						<a href="https://lithub.com/how-the-enslaved-of-saint-domingue-struck-fear-into-the-hearts-of-the-ruling-class/" title="How the Enslaved of Saint-Domingue Struck Fear Into the Hearts of the Ruling Class"><img class="story-img" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/La_partie_Francoise_de_lisle_de_Saint_Domingue_2674966926-1-300x300.jpg"></a>
					</div>
					<div class="story-content-container">
						<h2><a href="https://lithub.com/how-the-enslaved-of-saint-domingue-struck-fear-into-the-hearts-of-the-ruling-class/" title="How the Enslaved of Saint-Domingue Struck Fear Into the Hearts of the Ruling Class">How the Enslaved of Saint-Domingue Struck Fear Into the Hearts of the Ruling Class</a></h2>
					</div>
				</div>
